            "body": "Summary: short messages may be hidden if 'showmode' is enabled.\n\nMissing from the repro: the screen width needs to be narrow, so that the long `:args` message produces a multiline message.\n\nWith Nvim HEAD I also needed `strict=false`: `nvim_buf_get_lines(..., false)`\n\n- ui2 didn't help\n- `vim.schedule(function() vim.cmd.args() end)` didn't help",
